                    <h2 class="mb-4">Témoignages clients</h2>
                    <p>Pas <b>encore</b> convaincu ? Regardez ce que disent nos derniers clients de nous.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row ftco-animate justify-content-center">
                <div class="col-md-12">

                    <div class="carousel-testimony owl-carousel">
                        {% for review in reviews %}
                        <div class="item">
                            <div class="testimony-wrap d-flex">
                                <div class="user-img" style="background-image: url({{ '../uploads/pictures/'}}{{ review.picture }})">
                                </div>
                                <div class="text pl-4">
